Project description:

I have done every items on the checklist.

I use sort for painter's algorithm

For the final game:
(1) action: move up left down right and diagonal direction.
(2) blank to shoot bullet, eliminate enemy "zaku" and vessel.
(3) It will have a boss, a evil gundam.
(4) special weapon is laser ray, it can eliminate a lot of enemies.
(5) eliminate "Zaku" get 10 points, eliminate vessel give 30 points and special weapon.
(6) hit by enemies will reduce health.
(7) kill boss win.
(8) I will redesign the motion and weapon animation sheets to make them looks good
(9) maybe I will add more features depents on how far I can get




